These things happen.

353
00:17:08,344 --> 00:17:09,694
And have you met our son?

354
00:17:09,762 --> 00:17:11,356
He lunges headfirst
into everything.

355
00:17:11,380 --> 00:17:12,808
It's a wonder this
never happened sooner.

356
00:17:12,832 --> 00:17:14,464
Well, we can't go
back to that park.

357
00:17:14,533 --> 00:17:17,146
They need, like, sand or
some of that soft turf stuff.

358
00:17:17,170 --> 00:17:19,581
I mean, who puts concrete
steps by a play space?

359
00:17:19,605 --> 00:17:20,783
It's completely irresponsible.

360
00:17:20,807 --> 00:17:22,773
It is a superficial cut.
He's gonna be fine.

361
00:17:22,842 --> 00:17:24,152
I'm already late for my meeting.

362
00:17:24,176 --> 00:17:25,976
I can't just stick
him in daycare.

363
00:17:26,045 --> 00:17:29,179
Slow down. Slow down, okay?

364
00:17:29,248 --> 00:17:30,793
Now, we're gonna
figure this out.

365
00:17:30,817 --> 00:17:34,151
And, by the way, daycare
has very capable teachers.

366
00:17:34,220 --> 00:17:36,987
Oh, please. I am capable.

367
00:17:37,056 --> 00:17:39,084
So, your text said, "Make
sure the phase 3 patients go."

368
00:17:39,108 --> 00:17:41,392
Go to the bathroom? Go away?

369
00:17:41,461 --> 00:17:42,938
Sorry. I didn't
realize. Is he okay?

370
00:17:42,962 --> 00:17:44,590
Yes. No.

371
00:17:44,614 --> 00:17:46,508
Do you want me to reschedule
the phase 3 patient meetings today,

372
00:17:46,532 --> 00:17:47,993
maybe try to squeeze
them in next week, or...

373
00:17:48,017 --> 00:17:50,534
No, just...

374
00:17:50,603 --> 00:17:52,781
Ross, will you take them?
You understand the procedure.

375
00:17:52,805 --> 00:17:54,572
You know what to do. Just...

376
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:56,535
You know, I want you to
take over phase 3 from here.

377
00:17:56,559 --> 00:17:58,225
What? Are you sure?

378
00:17:58,294 --> 00:18:01,345
Yes. Can you do this for
me? Just do this for me, okay?

379
00:18:01,414 --> 00:18:04,148
Of course, if that's
what you want.

380
00:18:16,913 --> 00:18:20,214
I can't believe
Bailey's already seven.

381
00:18:20,282 --> 00:18:22,717
Please tell me he has
outgrown that whole

382
00:18:22,785 --> 00:18:24,819
"I fiddle with my
junk 24/7" phase,

