and do that job.

392
00:18:57,754 --> 00:19:00,054
I'm so tired.

393
00:19:00,123 --> 00:19:01,856
It's like I'm
sleepwalking all the time.

394
00:19:01,924 --> 00:19:05,158
Well, you're well into
your second trimester now,

395
00:19:05,227 --> 00:19:06,772
