00:19:37,827 --> 00:19:40,160
No.

405
00:19:40,229 --> 00:19:41,579
Maybe.

406
00:19:41,647 --> 00:19:44,548
Okay. But just a minute.

407
00:19:44,617 --> 00:19:45,916
And then nerves of steel.

408
00:19:46,518 --> 00:19:47,562
Right?

409
00:19:47,586 --> 00:19:48,586
Right.

410
00:19:48,654 --> 00:19:49,894
Okay.

411
00:19:52,525 --> 00:19:55,709
<i>The surgical mind needs
to be constantly inspired,</i>

412
00:19:55,778 --> 00:19:58,595
