to remove the vent?

441
00:22:26,278 --> 00:22:28,156
Ah!

442
00:22:28,180 --> 00:22:29,220
Son of a...

443
00:22:30,166 --> 00:22:31,565
Hey, you.

444
00:22:31,634 --> 00:22:33,211
